### Pipeline tracker + recent runs
GET http://localhost:4104/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=name eq 'ShipmentArchive'&$expand=runs($orderby=startTime desc;$top=5)

### Status function
GET http://localhost:4104/pipeline/status(name='ShipmentArchive')

### Flush — clears the remote target (O(n) DELETEs) and resets the tracker.
POST http://localhost:4104/pipeline/flush
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ShipmentArchive"}
